Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:47.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}总会有一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:50.65,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}飘落下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:56.45,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}属于我的蓝色天使啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:03:03.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}啊　那擦肩而过的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:08.19,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}弯下身去发现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:15.03,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}转身去呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:21.37,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}现在的内心里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:26.20,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}就像雪一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.73,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}堆积起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:33.30,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}纯真的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:38.40,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}就算绕了些远
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:40.98,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}这份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:46.34,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}也想直接亲口告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.30,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}总会有一日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:53.00,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}飞向蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:58.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}属于我的蓝色天使啊…
Dialogue: 2,0:02:45.59,0:02:47.56,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}いつからか
Dialogue: 2,0:02:48.70,0:02:50.65,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}舞い降りた
Dialogue: 2,0:02:51.73,0:02:56.45,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}私の蒼い天使よ…
Dialogue: 2,0:02:57.68,0:03:03.16,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}Ah　すれ違う微笑みに
Dialogue: 2,0:03:04.03,0:03:08.19,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}うつむくしかできずに
Dialogue: 2,0:03:10.20,0:03:15.03,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}背中ごしに声かけたの
Dialogue: 2,0:03:15.41,0:03:21.37,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}今は心の中で
Dialogue: 2,0:03:21.46,0:03:26.20,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}それは雪のように
Dialogue: 2,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.73,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}降りつもった
Dialogue: 2,0:03:29.09,0:03:33.30,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}イノセントな痛み
Dialogue: 2,0:03:33.63,0:03:38.40,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}たとえ遠まわりでも
Dialogue: 2,0:03:38.66,0:03:40.98,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}この想いは
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.33,0:03:46.34,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}まっすぐ届けたい
Dialogue: 2,0:03:47.16,0:03:49.30,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}いつの日か
Dialogue: 2,0:03:50.18,0:03:53.00,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}飛びたってゆけ
Dialogue: 2,0:03:53.32,0:03:58.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}私の蒼い天使よ…
