Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂家果然很了不得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还招待我们来这种规模的温泉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了这么多人  可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  非常欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像这温泉跟父亲的公司有些联系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是免费入场的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.23,0:00:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何时候都可以请你们来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏威夷和迪拜的温泉也是免费入场的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这一瞬间我体会到了差距
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂真是凌驾我们标准之上啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这么说  还真是让人瞠目结舌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:00:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始强攻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.40,0:01:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起尺寸更重要的是敏感度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏感度？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏感度？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏感度…是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.34,0:01:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚  亏你能静得下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.33,0:01:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  像你这么坐立不安更奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在桂她们全在旁边的温泉里入浴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人之心在亢奋  你就不想看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.03,0:01:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不能付诸于行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.07,0:01:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当这是漫画啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直要发疯了  就这样站着…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}好了…好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:02:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这水很舒服哦  不进来吗  这里是混浴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  混浴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混浴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你们的  真单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好下流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样算是幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个想法说明我们还是太年轻了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人节？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已经到这个时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  世界准备怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没什么特别要做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒谎  那个不给伊藤么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  给诚的是人情巧克力  人情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上这么说  其实是真命巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能  倒是光你准备怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.09,0:04:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑田终于要跟泽永告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没到这个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要给的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在考虑「该怎么办呢」的阶段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只给巧克力的话太可惜了  这可是个好机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  看上泽永  黑田的趣味还真不雅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两人也是  真容易看穿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界  客人们都看着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是为情人节做准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐不准备给谁巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是巧克力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把年纪了  还情人节？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人不管到了几岁也是少女哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是世界  你有中意的男孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:05:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我孩子  心里想的都写在脸上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我教你  作巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我不擅长做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那没关系  重要的是心意  心意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  还有就是印象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能做出一旦入口就回味无穷的那种味道的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做成这样的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能深深地刺入他的心窝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要刺进去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  直捣心窝  需要主动出击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不会出击的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击  出击  出击…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふんぐるい　むぐるうなふ\Nくとぅるふ　るるいえ  うが·なぐる　ふたぐん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふんぐるい　むぐるうなふ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}（咒语，意为邪神Cthulhu的归来）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  加纳的可可块不能立即到货
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那就没办法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只能用现有的东西做了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要  人鱼的眼泪和…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个也放进去吧  曼佗罗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人节当天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天2月14日的恋爱运是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「意想不到会是她积极主动地来接近你」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来  在进教室前没任何人给你东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还期待着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:08:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  怀着对我爱慕之心的少女是个怕羞的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「并且会同意和你一起跨过成人的那道坎」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚  成人的那道坎是什么滋味的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再去看一下鞋箱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前也好好看一下桌子里面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}没有  没有  完全没有  连渣都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  青春这个混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以打扰一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:08:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不太好  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要一个人跨过成人的那道坎吗  诚这个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  虽说我和伊藤之间事到如今才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这场景不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…难道…难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人情巧克力  人情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今给伊藤这种人也真是失败
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  你也是人情版的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是啊  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人情的 人情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  人情啊  什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.07,0:10:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那个是人情巧克力的  没必要收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚  加藤同学的那个是人情的吧  是人情的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优柔寡断
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个总之先静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是特意通宵做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:11:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊  考虑了3天3夜才选好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要收下的话不管哪个只能选一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个都是人情的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我为了诚君  努力做出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的对手出现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么要出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做巧克力真是很难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说  这个好像不是人情的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今  今天就收下这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤…  诚…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚君…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选哪个我都得死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  诚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个不注意  又到哪里去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}喂  那手上是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚  你在说什么胡话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不和姐姐一～起～吃～吗～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么世界的妈妈也来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下我吧  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连小心都…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来救救我～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无处可逃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚君  我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐来告诉你成人之礼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一辈子都可以叫你「哥哥」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  要我只选一个怎么都…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不痛快的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下有那种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  把大家的都吃了吧  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然会有不少神秘的味道  肯定是好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感想和答复  请等下次…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  白色情人节？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真期待下个月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于解放了  到底要怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  是清浦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「什么嘛」可真失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你吓我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做亏心事  不怕鬼敲门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可以这么做  但也不能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:14:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  拳击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.53,0:15:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要误会  是人情巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这样  是吗  是人情的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要的话…也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜  真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你  我精神多了  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  既然有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个才是来真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着  清浦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心意我领了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是当面给会害羞  我也是受人之托
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁  谁的…委托？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽永…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实比小说还突然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样算是幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个想法  说明我们还是太年轻了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的青春  坠向更深的混沌之中…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:17:04.42,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}忘れてたこんな気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:10.79,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;11;0,{\frz-90}閉じられた扉の奥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:18.50,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}鍵をかけ　開け方もわすえてしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:23.18,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}わたしのこころ　ほどけてゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:30.89,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}それはあなたの魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:37.23,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}指が笑顔が声が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:45.00,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}いつのまにか開けてしまう　素敵だね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:51.21,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}隣には優しい瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:58.06,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}ずっと　さがしてた言葉を
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:18:04.42,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}いつまでも言えずにいた　けれど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:11.32,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}kiss me,baby　キスして　やさしく
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:17.65,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}ほほに陽だまりの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:24.60,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}淡いぬくもりを残して
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:27.92,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}ずっとずっと二人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:30.85,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}歩こう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:17:04.42,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}早已忘却的这份感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:10.79,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;11;0,{\frz-90}藏在紧闭心门的深处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:18.50,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}紧紧锁住　甚至忘记如何开启
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:23.18,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}我的心扉　渐渐敞开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:30.89,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}被你的魔法唤醒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:37.23,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}你的手指　笑容和声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:45.00,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}悄悄叩开我的心　美妙绝伦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:51.21,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}身旁是你温柔的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:58.06,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}寻觅已久的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:18:04.42,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}羞于启齿　却要鼓起勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:11.32,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\rEDJ\frz-90}kiss{\fscx50}　{\fscx100}me,baby{\rEDC\frz-90}　给我温柔的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:17.65,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}脸庞印上朝阳的吻痕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:24.60,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}伴着淡淡的温馨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:27.92,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}两人相依而行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:30.85,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}直到永远
